data.description: Prime location, minutes from the VRE, Belmont Bay, Historic Occoquan, Shopping, Potomac Mills mall and interstate 95. Come view this 13,500-gallon in-ground pool with depths ranging from 3.5 to 5.5 feet, accessible from the primary bedroom. The detached garage and shed provide ample storage space for your outdoor or indoor essentials. With an assumable 3% loan, this home offer's both convenient and affordability. The primary bedroom, featuring patio doors that opens to the outdoor pool. While the landscaping is in good condition, there's potential to enhance and personalize the outdoor space to suit your preferences.  Water heater was replaced in 2017, and the HVAC lasted service in 2010. Home warranty carries over.
